Ụbọchị mba ụwa nke enweghị akwụna (IDNP) bụ ụbọchị mmata a na-eme iji megide omume mmekọahụ. Á hụrụ ya izizi na 2002, ihe omume a na-eme kwa afọ na 5th nke Ọktoba.
Ahụrụ IDNP izizi na 2002; n'oge afọ mmeghe ya, e mere ihe omume iji mata ya na San Francisco Bay Area nke California, na Melbourne, Victoria.

N'afọ 2005, Mahadum nke Philippines Institute of Human Rights na ngalaba Asia-Pacific nke Coalition Against Trafficking in Women (CATW) haziri ihe omume IDNP ébé ha nọ wéré Tyler maka Anti-Trafficking in Persons Act nke 2003. N'afọ 2008, e nwere nche ọkụ kandụl IDNP na Phoenix, Arizona; nche nke abụọ dị otú ahụ mere ọzọ n'afọ 2010 n'otu ebe ahụ, ya na ụfọdụ ndị isi obodo ahụ na ụfọdụ ndị bụbu ndị ọrụ mmekọahụ n'etiti ndị sonyere.
Nakwa na 2010, CATW hụrụ IDNP site na imegide mkpebi ahụ na Bedford v

Canada iji tie iwu Canada na-emegide ọrụ mmekọahụ. Otu ndị izizi na ndị na-azụ ahịa mmadụ na ndị bụbu ndị ọrụ mmekọahụ na ọbọdọ Canada megidere ịkụda iwu ndị a, na-eme ngagharị iwe n'ụlọ ikpe dị n'ime obodo Toronto, Ontario iji mara IDNP.
N'afọ 2011, People Working Against Prostitution, otu nzukọ na Philippines, gosipụtara ndakpọ olileanya na kansụl obodo Cagayan de Oro emeghị ihe omume ọ bụla iji mara IDNP.
